		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wonder if all these SFC to SNES adapters connected all 62 pins, not just the 48 middle pins.  Any modern adapter sold by Retrozone would, of course, have 62 contacts.  I can imagine some adapters sold back in the day decided to go cheap and omit the 16-extension pins.

		

		</td>
